overview.en: Coin Fubo is a block chain technology developed and operated by the BFB project team. It pays for digital money wallets + people's lives + digital currency C2C transactions + digital asset finance + digital assets of mainstream business forms, etc.. A pan-ecological block chain landing application project for the main service direction.
overview.zh: 币富宝是由BFB项目团队开发和运营的一个基于区块链技术的，以数字货币钱包+人们生活层面支付+数字货币C2C交易+数字资产理财+主流商业形态数字资产化等等，为主要服务方向的泛生态区块链落地应用项目。
